Interface NavigationManager.Listener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NavigationManager.ListenerAdapter
    Enclosing class:
    NavigationManager
    Deprecated. 
    As of SDK 2.1.1. See individual callback methods for alternatives.

    @Deprecated
public static interface NavigationManager.Listener
    Interface to report NavigationManager events
